#: ../../../quickstart.rst:8
msgid "Quickstart"
msgstr "快速入門"

#: ../../../quickstart.rst:10
msgid ""
"This page gives a brief introduction to the library. It assumes you have the "
"library installed, if you don't check the :ref:`installing` portion."
msgstr ""
"本頁提供此程式庫的簡要介紹。它假設您已經安裝了程式庫，如果尚未安裝，請參閱 :"
"ref:`installing` 章節。"

#: ../../../quickstart.rst:14
msgid "A Minimal Bot"
msgstr "最小化機器人"

#: ../../../quickstart.rst:16
msgid ""
"Let's make a bot that responds to a specific message and walk you through it."
msgstr "讓我們建立一個會回應特定訊息的機器人，並逐步帶您了解。"

#: ../../../quickstart.rst:18
msgid "It looks something like this:"
msgstr "它看起來像這樣："

#: ../../../quickstart.rst:20
msgid ""
"# This example requires the 'message_content' intent.\n"
"\n"
"import discord\n"
"\n"
"intents = discord.Intents.default()\n"
"intents.message_content = True\n"
"\n"
"client = discord.Client(intents=intents)\n"
"\n"
"@client.event\n"
"async def on_ready():\n"
"    print(f'We have logged in as {client.user}')\n"
"\n"
"@client.event\n"
"async def on_message(message):\n"
"    if message.author == client.user:\n"
"        return\n"
"\n"
"    if message.content.startswith('$hello'):\n"
"        await message.channel.send('Hello!')\n"
"\n"
"client.run('your token here')"
msgstr ""
"# 此範例需要 'message_content' 意圖。\n"
"\n"
"import discord\n"
"\n"
"intents = discord.Intents.default()\n"
"intents.message_content = True\n"
"\n"
"client = discord.Client(intents=intents)\n"
"\n"
"@client.event\n"
"async def on_ready():\n"
"    print(f'我們已以 {client.user} 身份登入')\n"
"\n"
"@client.event\n"
"async def on_message(message):\n"
"    if message.author == client.user:\n"
"        return\n"
"\n"
"    if message.content.startswith('$hello'):\n"
"        await message.channel.send('Hello!')\n"
"\n"
"client.run('在此輸入您的 token')"

#: ../../../quickstart.rst:45
msgid ""
"Let's name this file ``example_bot.py``. Make sure not to name it ``discord."
"py`` as that'll conflict with the library."
msgstr ""
"讓我們將此檔案命名為 ``example_bot.py``。請確保不要將其命名為 ``discord."
"py``，因為這會與程式庫產生衝突。"

#: ../../../quickstart.rst:48
msgid "There's a lot going on here, so let's walk you through it step by step."
msgstr "這裡有很多內容，讓我們逐步帶您了解。"

#: ../../../quickstart.rst:50
msgid ""
"The first line just imports the library, if this raises a :exc:"
"`ModuleNotFoundError` or :exc:`ImportError` then head on over to :ref:"
"`installing` section to properly install."
msgstr ""
"第一行只是匯入程式庫，如果這引發了 :exc:`ModuleNotFoundError` 或 :exc:"
"`ImportError`，請前往 :ref:`installing` 章節進行正確安裝。"

#: ../../../quickstart.rst:52
msgid ""
"Next, we create an instance of a :class:`Client`. This client is our "
"connection to Discord."
msgstr ""
"接下來，我們建立一個 :class:`Client` 的實例。此 client 是我們與 Discord 的連"
"線。"

#: ../../../quickstart.rst:53
msgid ""
"We then use the :meth:`Client.event` decorator to register an event. This "
"library has many events. Since this library is asynchronous, we do things in "
"a \"callback\" style manner."
msgstr ""
"然後我們使用 :meth:`Client.event` 裝飾器來註冊事件。此程式庫有許多事件。由於"
"此程式庫是異步的，我們以「回呼」（callback）風格的方式來處理事情。"

#: ../../../quickstart.rst:56
msgid ""
"A callback is essentially a function that is called when something happens. "
"In our case, the :func:`on_ready` event is called when the bot has finished "
"logging in and setting things up and the :func:`on_message` event is called "
"when the bot has received a message."
msgstr ""
"回呼本質上是一個在特定事件發生時被呼叫的函式。在我們的例子中，:func:"
"`on_ready` 事件會在機器人完成登入與設定後被呼叫，而 :func:`on_message` 事件則"
"在機器人收到訊息時被呼叫。"

#: ../../../quickstart.rst:59
msgid ""
"Since the :func:`on_message` event triggers for *every* message received, we "
"have to make sure that we ignore messages from ourselves. We do this by "
"checking if the :attr:`Message.author` is the same as the :attr:`Client."
"user`."
msgstr ""
"由於 :func:`on_message` 事件會對*每則*收到的訊息觸發，我們必須確保忽略來自自"
"己的訊息。我們透過檢查 :attr:`Message.author` 是否與 :attr:`Client.user` 相同"
"來做到這一點。"

#: ../../../quickstart.rst:62
msgid ""
"Afterwards, we check if the :class:`Message.content` starts with "
"``'$hello'``. If it does, then we send a message in the channel it was used "
"in with ``'Hello!'``. This is a basic way of handling commands, which can be "
"later automated with the :doc:`./ext/commands/index` framework."
msgstr ""
"之後，我們檢查 :class:`Message.content` 是否以 ``'$hello'`` 開頭。如果是，則"
"在使用該指令的頻道中發送 ``'Hello!'``。這是一種基本的指令處理方式，之後可以使"
"用 :doc:`./ext/commands/index` 框架來自動化處理。"

#: ../../../quickstart.rst:65
msgid ""
"Finally, we run the bot with our login token. If you need help getting your "
"token or creating a bot, look in the :ref:`discord-intro` section."
msgstr ""
"最後，我們使用登入 token 來執行機器人。如果您需要取得 token 或建立機器人的協"
"助，請查閱 :ref:`discord-intro` 章節。"

#: ../../../quickstart.rst:69
msgid ""
"Now that we've made a bot, we have to *run* the bot. Luckily, this is simple "
"since this is just a Python script, we can run it directly."
msgstr ""
"現在我們已經建立了一個機器人，我們必須*執行*它。幸運的是，這很簡單，因為這只"
"是一個 Python 腳本，我們可以直接執行它。"

#: ../../../quickstart.rst:72
msgid "On Windows:"
msgstr "在 Windows 上："

#: ../../../quickstart.rst:74
msgid "$ py -3 example_bot.py"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../quickstart.rst:78
msgid "On other systems:"
msgstr "在其他系統上："

#: ../../../quickstart.rst:80
msgid "$ python3 example_bot.py"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../quickstart.rst:84
msgid "Now you can try playing around with your basic bot."
msgstr "現在您可以試著玩玩看您的基本機器人了。"
